WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.867 --> 00:00:04.003 line:0%
(Hudson)
[as Dazzle]
Sorry it had to be this way.

00:00:04.036 --> 00:00:06.539 line:0%
Also, you should know
I'm your father.

00:00:06.572 --> 00:00:09.942 align:start position:0%
Daddy,
forgive me stealing bike.

00:00:09.975 --> 00:00:11.578 align:end position:100%
Keep going!
It's just locusts!

00:00:14.713 --> 00:00:16.349
Should we chase after the set?

00:00:16.382 --> 00:00:19.619
No.
The desert is now our set.

00:00:19.652 --> 00:00:22.622
[intense electronic music]

00:00:22.655 --> 00:00:30.597
♪ ♪

00:00:39.538 --> 00:00:40.973
(Dazzle)
All right, Hudson!

00:00:41.006 --> 00:00:45.111
When we cut the wheel loose,
you run like hell...

00:00:45.144 --> 00:00:46.512
because it will crush you!

00:00:46.545 --> 00:00:47.713 align:start position:0%
Why is it so big?

00:00:47.746 --> 00:00:49.082 align:start size:75% position:25%
It's forced perspective.

00:00:49.115 --> 00:00:50.983
It's gonna look normal size
on camera.

00:00:51.016 --> 00:00:52.985
Now, crew,
this goes without saying,

00:00:53.018 --> 00:00:56.456
but please do not fight
the rebels during the take.

00:00:56.489 --> 00:00:58.624
I know you're in a violent
struggle for your homeland,

00:00:58.657 --> 00:01:00.026
but I need your hustle, okay?

00:01:00.059 --> 00:01:03.430
Lights, camera, actualize
the events from the script!

00:01:08.968 --> 00:01:10.870
[screams]

00:01:10.903 --> 00:01:13.239
[groans]

00:01:13.272 --> 00:01:14.440 align:start position:0%
Oh, no!
Money!

00:01:14.473 --> 00:01:16.943 align:start position:0%
I mean, Zephyr,
I didn't mean to crush you.

00:01:16.976 --> 00:01:19.545 align:end position:100%
No feelings of hardness,
my friend.

00:01:19.578 --> 00:01:23.583 align:end position:100%
Your reenactment is only work
of value I ever produce.

00:01:23.616 --> 00:01:26.552 align:end position:100%
Promise me two things.
[coughs]

00:01:26.585 --> 00:01:29.122 align:end position:100%
You will finish
this reenactment,

00:01:29.155 --> 00:01:31.757 align:end position:100%
and you will bring Zephyr
back to life!

00:01:31.790 --> 00:01:34.227 align:start position:0%
Unless they discover a cure
for crushed body,

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:35.862
I can only promise the first.

00:01:35.895 --> 00:01:37.230 align:start size:31% position:69%
This true.

00:01:37.263 --> 00:01:38.664
There's blood in the streets.

00:01:38.697 --> 00:01:40.700 align:start size:63% position:38%
Don't forget to buy.

00:01:40.733 --> 00:01:43.569 align:start size:25% position:75%
[groans]

00:01:43.602 --> 00:01:46.139 size:84% position:42%
All right, let's clear this
corpse and go right away.

00:01:46.172 --> 00:01:47.740 align:start position:0%
Big smiles.
Why aren't we shooting?

00:01:47.773 --> 00:01:49.175
[gunfire]

00:01:49.208 --> 00:01:50.543 align:start size:47% position:53%
Zephyr is dead!

00:01:50.576 --> 00:01:54.614 align:end position:100%
The cruelest among us will now
fill the power vacuum!

00:01:54.647 --> 00:01:55.982 size:78% position:39%
Stop shooting each other!

00:01:56.015 --> 00:01:57.450
Save your ammo for the rebels!

00:01:57.483 --> 00:01:58.885
[helicopter blades whirring]

00:01:58.918 --> 00:02:01.354
[gunfire]

00:02:01.387 --> 00:02:03.956 align:end position:100%
Hudson!
Jump on the Novak-cam!

00:02:03.989 --> 00:02:04.989 align:end position:100%
Ho!
To freedom!

